text: Yvonne Oldfield is a former Jamaican cricketer. She made her Women's One Day International debut during the 1973 Women's Cricket World Cup against Young England in a group stage match where fellow Jamaican players Grace Williams, Madge Stewart, Elaine Emmanual, L McIntosh, Evelyn Bogle and Dorrett Davis also made their maiden international appearance in the inaugural Women's Cricket World Cup. == References == == External links == * Category:Possibly living people Category:Year of birth missing Category:Date of birth missing Category:Jamaican women cricketers Category:West Indian women cricketers
